Now's the time to make a play date with the game that's literally crawling with fun! 50 baby-filled levels of cuteness — that's, like, a bazillion baby toes! Tend to your babies' every need with five priceless inventions beyond every mother's dream Over 20 upgrades to buy, from stain-free walls to auto-rocking cradles
